{"tid":1507981,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【笑到最後】深圳超越香港，快點 - 高明","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:14:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a00a32e1318739b04e61f9f97186f7aa863b5fa","tid":1507981,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190826/20756252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20756252&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=dfa6ec93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20756252&h=98b984ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190826/20756252</a><br />\n<br />\n【笑到最後】深圳超越香港，快點 - 高明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190826/large/1566752398_7513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190826%2Flarge%2F1566752398_7513.jpg&h=2a14b5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生育、教育、醫療、擇業、置業、上市這些關鍵時刻的選擇，當香港不再成為選擇之列，便可以宣佈深圳已超越香港。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深圳要超越香港，彈指之間已可以做到，最簡單方法有兩個：一、將香港變成中國一個普通城市；二、中美貿易達成協議，中方遵守國際遊戲規則，開放市場、取消貿易壁壘、實行真正自由市場，當最終深圳特區改行普通法，香港連最後的優勢都會喪失，自然會被超越。<br />\n<br />\n近日中國國務院印發《關於支持深圳建設中國特色社會主義先行示範區的意見》，支持深圳建設「中國特色社會主義先行示範區」，重提深圳超越論。始終城市會發展，深圳已有不少東西超越了香港，任何以量取勝的東西，香港都不可能與深圳或其他中國城市匹敵。至於完全超越香港，只有一把尺可以量度香港是否被深圳取代，那把尺便是中國人。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴會否不來港上市，改到深圳上市？在港已上市的企業，會否立即取消H股地位？內地資金會否立即拋售香港的物業？香港的碩士、博士生會否不再是中國留學生為主？格隆滙、雪球、知乎之類，會否停止談論來港當醫生、教師、RO、會計、律師？每天150個單程證名額會否無人再願意來？單程證人來港，會否認為公屋質素太差，抽中後馬上放棄，然後回歸大灣區？孕婦來港作動，會否馬上急召海豚直昇機，飛到深圳醫院分娩，不想嬰兒取得香港出世紙？<br />\n<br />\n甚麼是超越？甚麼是取代？就是你在大是大非的情況之中，作出最理性的取捨，在上述一系例問題，生育、教育、醫療、擇業、置業、上市，全是人生關鍵時刻的選擇，當香港不再成為選擇之列，便可以宣佈深圳已超越香港。香港的優勢，只是一堆文件、一些承諾、及遵守這些承諾的慣例，完全開放源碼任抄。深圳超越香港，本欄的回應是：快點。<br />\n<br />\n高明<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/bigricetea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fbigricetea&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=61f7dbbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/bigricetea</a><br />\n本欄逢周一刊出 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【灣區風情】侵侵還有四大絕招 (程凱)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【滙海探戈】美元攬炒 金價看漲 (奇兵)"},{"pid":"a1856a8b6b2e93b65a1267b6b3c0be3ec1c123a2","tid":1507981,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=d8c2364b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=1cc589dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102458676557543/posts/1582783125191750?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102458676557543%2Fposts%2F1582783125191750%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bp